Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.98,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由行星同盟首都 海尼森波里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:09.59,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宅街 枫树岭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.21,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国防委员 优布·特留尼西特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.49,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军官候补生 达斯提·亚典波罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.98,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heinessenpolis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:09.59,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maple Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.21,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Job Trunicht
